# Express.js API — Practice Project

A personal practice project for learning how to build and consume a REST API using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Vue.js.

---

## What This Project Does

- Built a REST API from scratch using Express.js
- Connected to a local MongoDB database using Mongoose
- Implemented JWT authentication (register, login, protected routes)
- Consumed the API from a Vue.js frontend using Axios

---

## Tech Stack

**Backend**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB (local)
- Mongoose
- JSON Web Tokens (JWT)
- bcryptjs

**Frontend**
- Vue.js 3
- Axios
- Vue Router

